                    <span>I ordered this book primarily because Microsoft Press was not going to release their version for some time and I needed to learn the product.
<br />
<br />I found the information to be very informative and well written.
<br />
<br />I am looking forward to the release of the Advanced version which is due shortly.
<br />
<br />I would not hesitate to recommend this to anyone who needs to learn about Small Business Server 2003.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">1000 Pages should be 250</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
